  "summary": "The Public Non-Fungible Token Emote Repository standard provides an enhanced interactive utility for [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) and [ERC-1155](./eip-1155.md) by allowing NFTs to be emoted at. This proposal introduces the ability to react to NFTs using Unicode standardized emoji in a public non-gated repository smart contract that is accessible at the same address in all of the networks.",
